  3 EarthServerGenericClient.appendXYZASlider = function(element, moduleNumber){
  4     //X-Axis
  5     var XDiv = document.createElement("div");
  6     XDiv.setAttribute("id","EarthServerGenericClient_SliderCell_XDiv_" + moduleNumber );
  7     XDiv.innerHTML ="X Translation:";
  8     element.appendChild(XDiv);
  9     var XSlider = new Rj.widget.HorizontalSlider("#EarthServerGenericClient_SliderCell_XDiv_" + moduleNumber, -EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeX, EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeX);
 10     XSlider.addListener("hSliderListener", "valuechanged", function(value){
 11         EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.updateOffset(0,value);
 12     });
 13 
 14     var startValue = EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.models[moduleNumber].xOffset * EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeX;
 15     XSlider.$value = startValue;
 16     XSlider.$instantChange = true;
 17 
 18     //Y-Axis
 19     var YDiv = document.createElement("div");
 20     YDiv.setAttribute("id","EarthServerGenericClient_SliderCell_YDiv_" + moduleNumber );
 21     YDiv.innerHTML = "Y Translation:";
 22     element.appendChild(YDiv);
 23     var YSlider = new Rj.widget.HorizontalSlider("#EarthServerGenericClient_SliderCell_YDiv_" + moduleNumber, -EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeY, EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeY);
 24     YSlider.addListener("hSliderListener", "valuechanged", function(value){
 25         EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.updateOffset(1,value);
 26     });
 27 
 28     startValue = EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.models[moduleNumber].yOffset * EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeY;
 29     YSlider.$value = startValue;
 30     YSlider.$instantChange = true;
 31 
 32     //Z-Axis
 33     var ZDiv = document.createElement("div");
 34     ZDiv.setAttribute("id","EarthServerGenericClient_SliderCell_ZDiv_" + moduleNumber );
 35     ZDiv.innerHTML = "Z Translation:";
 36     element.appendChild(ZDiv);
 37     var ZSlider = new Rj.widget.HorizontalSlider("#EarthServerGenericClient_SliderCell_ZDiv_" + moduleNumber, -EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeZ, EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeZ);
 38     ZSlider.addListener("hSliderListener", "valuechanged", function(value){
 39         EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.updateOffset(2,value);
 40     });
 41 
 42     startValue = EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.models[moduleNumber].zOffset * EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.cubeSizeZ;
 43     ZSlider.$value = startValue;
 44     ZSlider.$instantChange = true;
 45 
 46     //AlphaChannel
 47     var ADiv = document.createElement("div");
 48     ADiv.setAttribute("id","EarthServerGenericClient_SliderCell_ADiv_" + moduleNumber );
 49     ADiv.innerHTML = "Transparency:";
 50     element.appendChild(ADiv);
 51     var ASlider = new Rj.widget.HorizontalSlider("#EarthServerGenericClient_SliderCell_ADiv_" + moduleNumber, 0, 100);
 52     ASlider.addListener("hSliderListener", "valuechanged", function(value){
 53         value = parseFloat(value/100);
 54         EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.updateTransparency(value);
 55     });
 56 
 57     startValue = EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.models[moduleNumber].transparency*100;
 58     ASlider.$value = startValue;
 59     ASlider.$instantChange = true;
 60 
 61 };

 63 EarthServerGenericClient.appendElevationSlider = function(element,moduleNumber){
 64     var Div = document.createElement("div");
 65     Div.setAttribute("id","EarthServerGenericClient_SPECIFICCell_Div_" + moduleNumber );
 66     Div.innerHTML = "Elevation:";
 67     element.appendChild(Div);
 68     var ElevationSlider = new Rj.widget.HorizontalSlider("#EarthServerGenericClient_SPECIFICCell_Div_" + moduleNumber, 0,100);
 69     ElevationSlider.addListener("hSliderListener", "valuechanged", function(value){
 70         EarthServerGenericClient_MainScene.updateElevation(value);
 71     });
 72     ElevationSlider.$value = 10;
 73     ElevationSlider.$instantChange = true;
 74 
 75 };

 77 EarthServerGenericClient.createProgressBar =  function(DivID)
 78 {
 79     $( DivID ).progressbar({ value: 0, max: 100 });
 80     $( DivID ).on( "progressbarcomplete", function( event, ui ) {
 81         $( DivID ).toggle( "blind" );
 82         } );
 83 
 84     this.updateValue = function(value)
 85     {
 86         $( DivID ).progressbar( "option", "value", value );
 87     };
 88 };
